<p>
While building several different applications it became clear that the built in serialize function did not quite
  satisfy all needs.  In particular, the CArchive module was actually deficient.  So I built the "Archive" module
  and all of CDoc supports opening and saving files on the serialize pattern.  Almost every function is virtual
  and can be replaced if needed in the application's document module.
  I'll use the template commands for open to describe how my version serialize works.
</p>

